videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Bowden lobs an alley-oop from the 3-point line for Yves Pons, who rises and smashes the dunk early in the first half.
videos.headline: Pons mashes alley-oop for Tennessee

videos.description: Tennessee's Grant Williams slips a backdoor bounce pass to Yves Pons who springboards for a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Pons backdoor cut leads to two-handed smash

videos.description: Grant Williams gets a Samford defender to bite on a pump fake, takes one dribble and slams home a vicious two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Williams throws down monstrous dunk

videos.description: Jordan Bone penetrates to the cup and dumps a quick pass to Admiral Schofield, who throws down the jam for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Schofield rips rim on pretty pass from Bone
